----------

  [1] QuickCheck: A Lightweight Tool for Random Testing of Haskell
      Programs.
      Koen Claessen and John Hughes.
      ICFP 2000.

  [2] QCheck/SML.
      Christopher League.
      [http://contrapunctus.net/league/haques/qcheck/]

  [3] xUnit.
      Wikipedia.
      [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XUnit]
